Sentencas: The electrochemical behaviour of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell (SOFC) was investigated by feeding a reformate of n-dodecane.
Titulo: Study of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell fed with n-dodecane reformate. Part I: Endurance test

Sentencas: Experiments were carried out at 800 degrees C by using a commercial-type cell with a composition Ni-YSZ/YSZ/YDC/LSFC and a chemical processor operating under Steam Reforming (SR) conditions at 800 degrees C, S/C equal to 2.5, and GHSV equal to 16,000 h(-1) in the presence of a commercial type catalyst based on Rh-CeO2-ZrO2.
Titulo: Study of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell fed with n-dodecane reformate. Part I: Endurance test

Sentencas: The composition of reformate gas was determined by gas-chromatography before the SOFC cell.
Titulo: Study of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell fed with n-dodecane reformate. Part I: Endurance test

Sentencas: An electrochemical lifetime test of 500 h for the coupled reformer-SOFC system demonstrated a good stability.
Titulo: Study of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell fed with n-dodecane reformate. Part I: Endurance test

Sentencas: EIS and polarizations curves were carried out during the endurance test.
Titulo: Study of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell fed with n-dodecane reformate. Part I: Endurance test

Sentencas: The catalyst of the chemical processor was analysed post-operation showing a negligible amount of carbon, whereas the discharged cell showed an increase of Ni particle size caused by the electrochemical ageing.
Titulo: Study of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell fed with n-dodecane reformate. Part I: Endurance test

Sentencas: A similar test was carried out under practical conditions with a large area SOFC showing a good stability characteristics and promising scale-up properties.
Titulo: Study of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell fed with n-dodecane reformate. Part I: Endurance test
